{"Title":"《窃读记》 朗读颗粒","LessonTitle":"窃读记","LessonAuthor":"刘淑娟","Reader":"张敏","Preview":"${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/assets/0a374eb1-4d80-4ced-8caa-4c18518d67e5.pkg/469e119c4b0b432abde242af14ff7115.png","Chapters":["1 窃读记"],"AudioAsset":"${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/assets/5e9c1ef7-d0f5-4f95-9170-84b5d5660d90.pkg/e506c51c77404810a285254c8346f5d5.ogg","SrtAsset":"${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/assets/a1a6de0a-3411-413e-ac0a-d326c72e9c7d.pkg/2948c828180f4124bf16a6418708c88c.srt","ImgsAsset":["${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/assets/0a374eb1-4d80-4ced-8caa-4c18518d67e5.pkg/469e119c4b0b432abde242af14ff7115.png"],"Phases":[{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"转过街角，看见饭店的招牌，闻见炒菜的香味，听见锅勺敲打的声音，我放慢了脚步。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":3.96,"EndTime":14.52},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":23,"WordCardId":"4c52f6ef-4182-4716-84a8-74a7d183515d","TeachMaterials":[]},{"WordIndex":15,"WordCardId":"0410a9d6-5159-4e5f-bcb4-712c9dd0f3c5","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"放学后急匆匆地从学校赶到这里，目的地可不是饭店，而是紧邻它的一家书店。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":15.24,"EndTime":25.52},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我边走边想：“昨天读到什么地方了？那本书放在哪里？左边第三排，不错……”","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":27.28,"EndTime":38.8},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"走到门口，便看见书店里仍像往日一样挤满了顾客。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":39.44,"EndTime":45.6},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我可以安心了。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":46.24,"EndTime":47.92},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"但我又担忧那本书会不会卖光，因为一连几天都看见有人买，昨天好像只剩下一两本了。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":48.6,"EndTime":59.24},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我跨进店门，暗喜没人注意。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":60.96,"EndTime":64.64},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我踮起脚尖，从大人的腋下挤过去。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":65.28,"EndTime":68.92},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":1,"WordCardId":"b24f2769-a01c-4a80-80e1-25058e083892","TeachMaterials":[]},{"WordIndex":10,"WordCardId":"bf5ad27c-bbc7-45f0-89e1-5c6f9a60d879","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"哟，把短发弄乱了，没关系，我总算挤到里边来了。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":69.72,"EndTime":75.88},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":0,"WordCardId":"b4d7f11f-3d7b-4421-8ca3-9837b41b0b89","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"在一排排花花绿绿的书里，我的眼睛急切地寻找，却找不到那本书。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":76.56,"EndTime":84.48},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"从头来，再找一遍。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":85.12,"EndTime":87.28},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"啊！它在这里，原来不在昨天的地方了。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":87.92,"EndTime":92.4},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"急忙打开书，一页，两页，我像一匹饿狼，贪婪地读着。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":94.04,"EndTime":100.96},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":16,"WordCardId":"238813eb-a267-4086-92f9-63937d7dd2b9","TeachMaterials":[]},{"WordIndex":20,"WordCardId":"b1e9ec81-8414-4fa7-b14a-fa9f6f9b75fd","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我很快乐，也很惧怕——这种窃读的滋味！","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":101.64,"EndTime":106.84},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":7,"WordCardId":"e5f8ba7d-7365-496e-a631-f09f22f53cd8","TeachMaterials":[]}]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我害怕被书店老板发现，每当我觉得当时的环境已不适宜再读下去的时候，我会知趣地放下书走出去，再走进另一家。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":108.52,"EndTime":120.56},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"有时，一本书要到几家书店才能读完。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":121.2,"EndTime":126.04},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我喜欢到顾客多的书店，因为那样不会被人注意。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":127.76,"EndTime":133.08},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"进来看书的人虽然很多，但是像我这样常常光顾而不从不购买的，恐怕没有。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":133.76,"EndTime":142.04},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"因此我要把自己隐藏起来。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":142.8,"EndTime":145.56},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"有时我会贴在一个大人的身边，仿佛我是他的小妹妹或小女儿。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":146.24,"EndTime":153.32},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"最令人开心的是下雨天，越是倾盆大雨我越高兴，因为那时我便有充足的理由在书店待下去。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":155.0,"EndTime":166.24},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":29,"WordCardId":"73fe9918-8bb6-449e-9f6c-feec2f9fa4d5","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"就像在屋檐下躲雨，你总不好意思赶我走吧？","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":166.88,"EndTime":171.56},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":4,"WordCardId":"b03656dd-3e66-42bc-bee6-11be61fb9342","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我有时还要装着皱起眉头，不时望着街心，好像说：“这雨，害得我回不去了。”","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":172.2,"EndTime":182.0},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":7,"WordCardId":"bb619a68-743a-44bc-961d-e2af1012fce7","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"其实，我的心里却高兴地喊着：“大些！再大些！”","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":182.44,"EndTime":188.56},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"当饭店飘来一阵阵菜香时，我已饿得肌肠辘辘，那时我也不免要做白日梦：如果口袋里有钱该多好！去吃一碗热热的面条，回到这里时，已经有人给摆上了一张沙发，坐上去舒舒服服地接着看。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":190.24,"EndTime":214.16},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":47,"WordCardId":"129c0543-44f8-40b5-8a32-13484cf6623b","TeachMaterials":[]},{"WordIndex":18,"WordCardId":"1b2704a1-d48c-41d4-b9b6-c4e4f7e18f3a","TeachMaterials":[]}]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我的腿真酸哪，不得不交替着用一条腿支撑着，有时又靠在书柜旁，以求暂时的休息。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":214.84,"EndTime":226.04},"WordCards":[{"WordIndex":18,"WordCardId":"d0f2b5ce-503f-4aff-b96b-1747e053e4c5","TeachMaterials":[]},{"WordIndex":4,"WordCardId":"c11ac94e-37b0-4a34-806a-68dc6bb3aec4","TeachMaterials":[]},{"WordIndex":27,"WordCardId":"c71876e0-e357-4ced-afd5-293b57d1a441","TeachMaterials":[]}]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"当书店的日光灯忽地亮了起来，我才发觉已经站在这里读了两个多钟头了。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":227.68,"EndTime":235.68},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我合上书，咽了一口唾沫，好像把所有的智慧都吞下去了，然后才依依不舍地把书放回书架。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":236.32,"EndTime":248.0},"WordCards":[]}]},{"PhaseInfo":"Phase","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"我低着头走出书店，脚站得有些麻木，我却浑身轻松。","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":249.76,"EndTime":256.96},"WordCards":[]},{"SentenceInfo":"句子信息","Text":"这时，我总会想起国文老师鼓励我们的话：“记住，你们是吃饭长大的，也是读书长大的！”","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":257.6,"EndTime":269.92},"WordCards":[]}]}],"Subject":[{"PhaseInfo":"Title","Sentences":[{"SentenceInfo":"标题信息","Text":"窃读记","Spell":"","TimeLine":{"StartTime":0.64,"EndTime":2.36},"WordCards":null}]}]}
